title: Catch me if you can - Year 1989 - Actor Matt Lattanzi
description:
Hi. My name is Hernan and i'm from Argentina. Been looking for this vhs-only movie for a long time. Hate Spielberg for making a movie of the same name! Made things more difficult! Now that i got it, i share it with you. Please seed it for at least a week. There some guys selling it over the net in DVD-r. I got the movie divided in 8 chapters. The problem is that when i join them, the audio and video don't match. If any of you can solve this, please let me download it off you!
Thanks to all of you off from whom i downloaded something, sometime. Bye.
